#: ../../project_and_asset_management/library.rst:255
msgid ""
"You can use the file manager of your choice to manage your library. Kdenli"
"ve simply reads the contents of the directory you specified in the setting"
"s. For more complex file management this is the recommended way. Changes t"
"o the library folder made outside of Kdenlive are reflected in near real-t"
"ime."
msgstr ""
"U kunt de bestandsbeheerder naar uw keuze gebruiken om uw bibliotheek te "
"beheren. Kdenlive leest eenvoudig de inhoud van de map die u specificeert "
"in de instellingen. Voor complexer beheer is dit de aanbevolen manier. "
"Wijzigingen aan de bibliotheekmap gedaan buiten Kdenlive worden bijna in "
"realtime meegenomen."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/library.rst:257
msgid ""
"For more complex renaming tasks use the file manager or bulk rename utilit"
"y of your choice. Changes to the library folder made outside of Kdenlive a"
"re reflected in near real-time."
msgstr ""
"Voor complexere taken voor hernoemen gebruik de bestandsbeheerder of "
"hulpmiddel voor in bulk hernoemen van uw keuze. Wijzigingen aan de "
"bibliotheekmap gemaakt buiten Kdenlive worden in bijna realtime "
"meegenomen."
